high_descs: Move forward and face the green table to your right.
Pick up the silver knife from the table in front of you.
Turn right, then right again and face the fridge in front of you.
Open the fridge, slice the potato inside and close it.
Turn right and look at the stove in front of you.
Put the silver knife on the counter to your left.
Turn around and face the fridge to your right.
Take a potato slice out of the fridge and close it.
Turn right and head to the microwave on top of the stove in front of you.
Heat up the potato in the microwave in front of you and take it out.
Turn around and face the sink to your right.
Put the potato in the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot potato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the fridge on the right.
Open the door, slice the potato on the shelf, and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the counter.
Place the knife on the counter to the left.
Turn around and walk back to the fridge on the right.
Open the door to the fridge. Take a potato slice and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the microwave above the stove.
Open the microwave door, put the potato slice inside, close the door, and turn on the microwave. Remove the slice when it's done and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Place the slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved potato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the green table on your right.
Pick up the knife in front of the wine bottle on the green table.
Turn to your right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and cut the potato inside it.
Turn to the right and walk just past the sink.
Place the knife on the counter just to the right of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and grab a piece of the cut up potato.
Turn right and walk to the microwave above the stove.
Microwave the piece of potato and then pick the piece of potato up.
Turn around and walk to the sink to the right of the fridge.
Place the piece of potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved piece of potato into the sink.

high_descs: Take a half step to your right and walk to the frying pan on the green table to your right and face it.
Pick up the knife to the left of the pan.
Turn right and walk to the fridge that's on your right and stand facing it.
Use the knife to cut the potato in the fridge into slices then close the door.
Turn right and take a step.
Put the knife on the counter to the right of the sink.
Walk back to the fridge.
Pick up  a slice of potato and make sure to close the fridge.
Turn right and take a step right and then walk to the stove.
Brown the slice of potato in the microwave and then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink that's on your right and stand facing the left side of it.
Put the slice of potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a browned slice of potato in the sink.
